Details:
The Princeton Review, Manya Abroad (Manya Education Private Ltd.) is a foreign education admissions service provider to Indian students for over a decade and is also a provider of Test Preparation for GMAT, GRE, SAT, ACT, AP, PSAT, and IELTS & TOEFL. However, some of the services provided by the company, such as Campus Recruitment services & Admissions counseling for IIMs, ISB, Great Lakes cater to students interested in pursuing higher education in India. Manya Education Private Limited (MEPL) was set up in 2002 with the vision to provide the best services in test preparation and admissions counseling to the Indian student who dreams to study abroad. Since then, MEPL has firmly established itself as the ultimate destination for International education and educational services in India. The Companys student base is steadily increasing across India, with over 20000 fresh students every year over the last 3 years (touching over 30000 in 2014). Since its inception in 2002, it has now grown to a network of 38 offices (21 cities) spread across Bangalore, Chandigarh, Chennai, Coimbatore, Dehradun, Gurgaon, Guwahati, Hyderabad, Jaipur, Kolkata, Lucknow, Ludhiana, Mangalore, Mysore, New Delhi, Noida, Trichy, Vellore, Vijayawada, Vishakhapatnam and Warangal; and it continues to expand. In 2014, the company opened its first International operation in Kathmandu, Nepal. 
Partners:- MEPL is the Indian partner of The Princeton Review (TPR), the worlds leading test preparation service provider for GMAT, GRE, SAT, IELTS and TOEFL. TPR is a US based company established in 1981 and is currently a premium global brand with a strong presence in 17 countries.

Details: This institute was founded by our honorary director Mr.A. NIRMAL,M.A., M.A., M.Phil., as an specialized center with a view to establish a bench-mark institution to achieve excellence in the toughest competitive exam in the country, i.e. Indian Administrative Service Exam which has now come to be known as Civil Services Exam. Our Honorary director Nirmals affiliation to the field of IAS examination for more than ten years, both as an aspirant and a teacher has made him to understand the nuances of all the three levels of IAS Examination viz., Preliminary, Mains and Interview. Being a post graduate in both History & Psychology, our director have been able to provide an insightful guidance for this examination. Over this long period, this IAS institute has evolved into a unique fraternity of educators and students striving together, year after year, in pursuit of a single goal. With a passion to excel, the Study Circle has raged with the dynamism of a river which constantly renews itself and yet remains unchanging in its resolve to reach its ultimate destination.Throughout a journey lasting over ten years, the academy has been at the cutting edge of real learning. Today, it is known as the most successful IAS academy in the country, performing consistently at high levels and has acquired the rare distinction of achieving the highest success-rate in the Civil Services Exam and acquired the status of best IAS academy in Trichy.The faculty team of the institute is composed of experienced educators, young IAS and IPS officers. In fact, the essence of the functioning of the academy is the fraternal atmosphere it provides, in which the students are groomed by a committed, imaginative and gifted core faculty team. Here, every student experiences creative excitement along with the thrill of adding to his store of knowledge. We treat each aspirant as a personality and not just a student. We approach our task like that of growing flowers; with all the will and skill required for performing such a delicate task. The aim is to set the students free from the rigidities of highly ritualized, blank and indifferent teaching that they have so far experienced in universities; where there is a lot of teaching but very little learning. This is the gap that this coaching institute strives to remove by promoting REAL LEARNING, i.e. learning about learning as the first step: with the ultimate aim of making the personalities bloom like flowers and carry the aroma of freshness of their ideas and creativity wherever they go. It is precisely because of this sense of commitment that this academys name has become a living legend among the students who are preparing for Civil Services examination.We provide excellent training in gaining conceptual knowledge in various subjects viz. General Studies, Sociology, Geography, Public Administration, History, Political Science and Psychology. The Academy facilitates many a candidate to achieve remarkable success in their career. The faculty members are highly qualified and are from reputed institutions. Approaching the subjects from the examination point of view, supplementing it with impeccable notes, periodical exams and in-depth review of answers is the key strength of the Academy.
